00:18:12.999 --> 00:18:17.125
Unless and until that person becomes aware of it, you don't say that.

00:18:17.417 --> 00:18:19.999
Because why frighten a person, for nothing at all?

00:18:20.291 --> 00:18:22.875
If she has done, if she is a disciple of Mine, I am surprised,

00:18:23.125 --> 00:18:25.999
you are not to tell people like that. But,

00:18:26.625 --> 00:18:29.834
slowly you can introduce and tell that this is to be done

00:18:30.333 --> 00:18:34.999
to get well, all right? Have you been to some guru?

00:18:36.208 --> 00:18:41.458
Y: No, I had certain

00:18:41.999 --> 00:18:46.999
visions and things that just came to me, when I was a bit younger.

00:18:47.709 --> 00:18:52.375
What sort of visions? Y: Little people, I saw little people,

00:18:53.291 --> 00:18:56.999
and what I was led to believe were nature spirits.

00:18:58.125 --> 00:19:01.333
I didn't want to see them, it just happened.

00:19:04.625 --> 00:19:07.291
SM: But you've been to some clairvoyant person or someone?

00:19:08.333 --> 00:19:13.417
Y: I think he claimed he was clairvoyant, but I knew he wasn't.

00:19:13.875 --> 00:19:16.417
SM: Must be something like that. Y: So I didn't believe him.

00:19:16.625 --> 00:19:18.083
SM: You see they're all like that.

00:19:18.250 --> 00:19:20.333
Clairvoyance is not a very great thing.

00:19:20.542 --> 00:19:23.583
If he says he's clairvoyant, then he must be.

00:19:24.041 --> 00:19:27.083
See if you go to these people, they push you to the left

00:19:27.125 --> 00:19:28.917
or to the right and you can see like that,

00:19:29.125 --> 00:19:31.208
you see they can they can go to any extent.

00:19:31.250 --> 00:19:34.333
Those who go to left side can see lots of things.

00:19:34.625 --> 00:19:37.291
Example I'll give you: a gentleman,

00:19:37.500 --> 00:19:41.333
who was one of our trustees, he was bringing another fellow

00:19:41.792 --> 00:19:46.375
who was mentally disturbed. He went to the station

00:19:47.083 --> 00:19:50.250
and this fellow did not arrive so he was rather upset.

00:19:50.750 --> 00:19:52.792
So he went to the post office to telephone.

00:19:53.125 --> 00:19:55.709
The phone was out of order, so another gentleman said

00:19:55.875 --> 00:19:58.083
there's a house there, you can go and ask them.

00:19:58.208 --> 00:19:59.917
They'll allow you to telephone.

00:20:00.000 --> 00:20:02.999
So when this telephoning the fellow came out and he said,

00:20:03.208 --> 00:20:05.458
"Why do you want to telephone to this man?"

00:20:05.917 --> 00:20:08.625
He told that, "I know you want to take him to Mother

00:20:08.875 --> 00:20:11.583
but you should not because Mother is doing a very great work,

00:20:11.709 --> 00:20:13.333
why do you want to take this fellow to her?

00:20:13.500 --> 00:20:14.500
Why do you want to trouble her?"

00:20:14.750 --> 00:20:16.917
He was surprised, how did he know all about this.

00:20:17.208 --> 00:20:22.333
They can read your minds. And he said, "No it's better that you go.

00:20:22.750 --> 00:20:26.999
Take this man to a temple somewhere outside Bombay

00:20:27.333 --> 00:20:32.166
and go and take one coconut and see the person

00:20:32.709 --> 00:20:35.333
who is in charge of the temple."

00:20:35.959 --> 00:20:39.999
So when he went with that coconut there, with this gentleman,

00:20:40.125 --> 00:20:43.333
he started telling all the stories without...

00:20:43.834 --> 00:20:47.333
They all were amazed both of them, how did they know all about it?

00:20:48.083 --> 00:20:52.583
So he took that coconut from him.

00:20:53.083 --> 00:20:55.999
And he said, "With this you have to give hundred rupees each."

00:20:56.417 --> 00:20:58.375
So they gave hundred rupees first to him.

00:20:58.542 --> 00:21:00.417
And it started off like that, you see.

00:21:00.709 --> 00:21:03.792
Till one day I came back from London.

00:21:04.083 --> 00:21:06.083
And I saw this and I said, "Where have you been?"

00:21:06.333 --> 00:21:08.333
He was just shaking before Me like this.

00:21:08.625 --> 00:21:11.125
So he said to know one, there was one gentleman in the temple,

00:21:11.333 --> 00:21:14.458
thing this that thing, I said, "What ? How did you do that?

00:21:14.792 --> 00:21:16.208
Why should you go to that place?"

00:21:16.417 --> 00:21:18.667
You see they can read minds and things.

00:21:18.917 --> 00:21:20.999
And ultimately that fellow never got cured,

00:21:21.333 --> 00:21:24.458
they lost all their money and this one died of heart.

00:21:26.625 --> 00:21:29.625
So it's a very common practice in India, everywhere,

00:21:29.959 --> 00:21:32.999
everywhere I find this a very common practice to use these spirits.

00:21:33.250 --> 00:21:36.083
Here also I find lots of people are going to these clairvoyant

00:21:36.375 --> 00:21:39.792
women and clairvoyant men and all that. It's very dangerous thing,

00:21:39.999 --> 00:21:44.291
one should not deal with that area which we do not know.

00:21:45.959 --> 00:21:50.375
Is a very common thing and apart from that you see like this -

00:21:50.999 --> 00:21:54.041
we have pentecostals, and that's all this same thing.

00:21:54.875 --> 00:21:58.291
We have pentecostals doing that ho ho ho ho ho ho stuff.

00:21:59.250 --> 00:22:02.333
Is nothing but that, because after all,

00:22:02.750 --> 00:22:08.375
if you have to get realized you become a decent person, isn't it?

00:22:10.834 --> 00:22:15.333
You become a sensible person, a saner person, a wiser person.

00:22:15.875 --> 00:22:20.375
You don't become a stupid fellow or you don't become an absurd

00:22:20.834 --> 00:22:23.166
and obtuse personality you don't develop, isn't it?

00:22:23.625 --> 00:22:26.458
We must also know that all such obtuse people

00:22:26.583 --> 00:22:28.750
cannot be realized souls, you see.

00:22:29.500 --> 00:22:34.625
They are funny faces, funny looking eyes

00:22:34.959 --> 00:22:37.208
and they are so greedy

00:22:37.834 --> 00:22:43.041
and they have no virtues, nothing, how can they be godly people?

00:22:43.792 --> 00:22:47.999
You should judge them by the way they live, by the style they live.

00:22:48.083 --> 00:22:54.250
You see a good man lives in a way that is very decent, decorous.

00:22:55.458 --> 00:23:00.792
Isn't it? Is the smallest thing that we should understand is that

00:23:03.083 --> 00:23:07.166
when God resides within us, when there is light,

00:23:07.999 --> 00:23:11.625
you see in every walk of such a man there is light.

00:23:12.583 --> 00:23:16.208
You should have compassion, love, if he's a hot-tempered fellow,

00:23:16.917 --> 00:23:20.375
furious style then how can,

00:23:22.083 --> 00:23:24.667
how can he be claim to be godly?

00:23:26.083 --> 00:23:29.999
We must use our brains, but when they come to Me

00:23:30.375 --> 00:23:32.625
only that time they start using in the other direction.

00:23:33.999 --> 00:23:36.959
Because you're free to use. It's all right, I am happy in a way

00:23:37.291 --> 00:23:39.999
that you use it because you should be free to use it.

