I said, "Now. I have to cook for so many people,

00:26:54.458 --> 00:26:57.458
what am I to do?" "All right," I said, "I'll talk to you."

00:26:57.834 --> 00:27:00.333
And I was amazed, the way he was ruined, you know.

00:27:00.875 --> 00:27:03.583
He was a rich man, he lost all his money, everything.

00:27:05.500 --> 00:27:08.792
